snippet.title: Maybe : Interactive Story | Long Live The Empress : The Curse and Love | Ep 01
snippet.description:
[NEW | ONGOING]
The curse of the dead befalls the Heath Empire. You, The Empress are told that sleeping with your consort is the only way to break the curse. But instead of bedding the betrothed your family chose to you, you decide to bring in a beautiful slave as your lover..

Who will you choose in the midst of the chaos the curse and its political battles bring?
